channel.title: How do You Create a Webclient?
channel.description:
Hello it's me linkey. Since my old account (Bloody4 FTW) got deleted somehow, I made this one.
First of All, Webclients are Easy to Get onto and Require no Downloads. They allow players to spend less time and less hassle when joining a server. I have currently just realeased a client and I would like it to be on a webclient. If you can help reply to me because it would be a big help to me. :)
If You can make one for me, I'll be glad to help you code your server/client to your liking. My client download is below. If you made it a Webclient just reply to me with a link taking it to the client.
Here is an Image of my Client and How I would like it to Look.
[IMG]http://i383.photobucket.com/albums/oo273/Canownueasy/Bloody4ScapeAllPurposeClient.jpg[/img]
If you would like to help me -- [url=http://www.mediafire.com/download.php?zh2qeai3m3z][b][size=15pt]Click Here[/size][/b][/url]
Thanks, Linkey(Bloody4 FTW)
